		<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/Icons/icon1.gif" border="0" align="ABSCENTER" width="15" height="15">
		<font size="2" face="Verdana">
		<font size="1" face="Verdana">posted 7/11/2003 11:07:57 AM&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;

		
		<a href="MB_editmsg.asp?FID=61&FN=Cleric&SID=7&SN=EverQuest&TID=1957688&TN=proper+healing+technique&CAT=Classes&SURL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Eeverlore%2Ecom&MSID=1995271&PL=4">
		<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/edit.gif" border="0" alt="Edit/Delete Message" width="18" height="13"></a>
		
		</font>
		<hr size="1">Proper healing tchniques 101</P><P>Best way to heal is to be prepared. If you paln on EXPing than I would make sure you have the proper spells lined up in your spell slots. Its really all about mana managment. Here is how I arrange mine:</P><P>1-Heal 1 (fast heal)<BR>2-Heal 2 (Heal for casters)<BR>3-Heal 3 (CH or big heal for Tanks)<BR>4-Heal over time<BR>5-Utility<BR>6-Yaulp if I paln on hitting or DD spell<BR>7-Atone or Mem blur type spell<BR>8-Root or DA </P><P>1. Fast Healing is an important skill...its used on bad pulls, repops, Trains. Experience is the only way to learn this skill</P><P>2. Heal for caster. Lets face it casters do not have much HP why waste big heal (big mana) spells on them.</P><P>3.CH or big heal spell is used on the MT. The MT will have large amount of HP and its best to fill up when the MT is down. Its all part of mana managment</P><P>4.Heal over time is a god send. Great to cast when you need to heal someone. Its low aggro and youcan med through it to cast another or bigger heal spell. Its another mana managment skill.</P><P>5.Utility can be a buff or a cure or what ever you need it to be</P><P>6.Yaulp if you are gong to attack or DD if you have some sort of clarity going</P><P>7.Atone(memblur)for those mobs that are rooted by you</P><P>8.DA or ROOT divine aura is a life saver. Root if you need to be the one to root mobs, if so make sure you have atone or a decrease aggor spell up it goes hand in hand.</P><P><BR>Hope this helps <img src='http://www.everlore.com/gimages/smile.gif' width=15 height=15 align=middle></P><P>Folic Acid "The People's Cleric of Brell" </P><P></P><P><br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
	</font>
